com.bigdata.relation.rule

Interface IStarJoin.IStarConstraint<E>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SPOStarJoin.SPOStarConstraint
    Enclosing interface:
    IStarJoin<E>

    public static interface IStarJoin.IStarConstraint<E>
    A star constraint specifies the shape of the star join. Star constraints will determine whether a particular element matches the constraint, and will create variable bindings for that elements.
